　　111 　年　　10　　月　　24　　日\r\n                            書記官  吳昌穆","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/PCEV/111%2c%e6%9d%bf%e7%b0%a1%2c1933%2c20221021%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"PCEV,111,板簡,1933,20221021,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"板簡","JNO":"1933","JDATE":"20221021","JTITLE":"清償借款"}